    "sections": [
        {
            "id": "block_50bba12076720a48ac737bca5c196075",
            "type": "heroTBM",
            "modifiers": ["animated-hero"],
            "heading": "A Contemporary JavaScript Calendar Toolkit",
            "body_html": "<p>The Bryntum Calendar is a contemporary calendar component offering multiple views. Written in pure JavaScript, it slots cleanly into <a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/react-calendar/\"><span class=\"s1\">React</span></a>, <a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/angular-calendar\"><span class=\"s1\">Angular</span></a> and <a href=\"https://bryntum.com/products/vue-calendar/\"><span class=\"s1\">Vue</span></a> apps.</p>",
            "body_text": "The Bryntum Calendar is a contemporary calendar component offering multiple views. Written in pure JavaScript, it slots cleanly into React , Angular and Vue apps.",
            "ctas": [
