        {
            "id": "block_dec4a474ba08484c3bd147cc587e5ce5",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Why Calendar?",
            "heading": "Why pick a JavaScript event Calendar?",
            "body_html": "<p>Built on JavaScript, a foundational web technology, the calendar component drops into existing applications with a ready-to-wire-up set of interactive features.</p> <p>Picking the Bryntum JavaScript Calendar gives your users a thoughtfully designed and high-performing calendar that has been thoroughly tested and battle-proven in production apps.</p>",
            "body_text": "Built on JavaScript, a foundational web technology, the calendar component drops into existing applications with a ready-to-wire-up set of interactive features. Picking the Bryntum JavaScript Calendar gives your users a thoughtfully designed and high-performing calendar that has been thoroughly tested and battle-proven in production apps.",
            "links": [],
            "ctas": [],
