        {
            "id": "block_7f8a8ef5340328b7601457cdd648ee6d",
            "type": "text-mini-demo",
            "eyebrow": "Try It Yourself",
            "heading": "Try It Live",
            "body_html": "<p class=\"pre-title\">Have a play yourself</p>  <p>The calendar handles recurring tasks out of the box. Repeat tasks on any cadence you need – daily, weekly, monthly or yearly.</p>",
            "body_text": "Have a play yourself  The calendar handles recurring tasks out of the box. Repeat tasks on any cadence you need – daily, weekly, monthly or yearly.",
            "ctas": [],
            "demo_kind": "calendar",
            "demo_position": "right"
        },
        {
            "id": "block_8f1c153294c4e8675efe148425adf91f",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Customisation",
            "heading": "Fully Tailorable",
            "body_html": "<p>The Bryntum Calendar is themed with CSS variables, so you can tweak its appearance to taste.</p> <ul class=\"ul1\"> <li>Pick one of our themes or <a href=\"/products/calendar/examples/custom-theme/\">roll your own</a>.</li> <li class=\"li1\">Adjust the rendering of <a href=\"/products/calendar/examples/custom-rendering/\">events, headings and more</a>.</li> <li class=\"li1\">Reflow the UI for <a href=\"/products/calendar/examples/month-agenda/\">mobile devices</a> with layouts that respond to any <a href=\"/products/calendar/examples/responsive/\">screen size</a>.</li> <li class=\"li1\">Drop links and buttons into <a href=\"/products/calendar/examples/tooltips/\">tailored tooltips</a>.</li> <li class=\"li1\">Customise the <a href=\"/products/calendar/examples/eventedit/\">event editor</a>, <a href=\"/products/calendar/examples/custom-menus/\">context menu</a> and <a href=\"/products/calendar/examples/sidebar-customization/\">sidebar</a>.</li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "The Bryntum Calendar is themed with CSS variables, so you can tweak its appearance to taste. Pick one of our themes or roll your own . Adjust the rendering of events, headings and more . Reflow the UI for mobile devices with layouts that respond to any screen size . Drop links and buttons into tailored tooltips . Customise the event editor , context menu and sidebar .",
            "links": [
                {
                    "text": "roll your own",
                    "href": "/products/calendar/examples/custom-theme/"
                },
                {
