        {
            "id": "block_a19229e400d243cafae6308f92930552",
            "type": "text-media",
            "modifiers": ["image", "added-shadow"],
            "eyebrow": "Component Library",
            "heading": "50+ Additional Widgets",
            "body_html": "<p class=\"p1\">Pick from a <a href=\"/products/calendar/examples/kitchen-sink/\">broad set of UI components</a> that quickly give your app a polished, professional feel:</p> <ul class=\"ul1\"> <li class=\"li1\">Drop in ready-made <strong>menus, toggles, sliders, charts and more</strong> alongside the Bryntum Calendar.</li> <li class=\"li1\">Cut clicks and searching to meet user needs faster.</li> <li class=\"li1\">Wire up and style widgets straightforwardly via our clear docs.</li> </ul>",
            "body_text": "Pick from a broad set of UI components that quickly give your app a polished, professional feel: Drop in ready-made menus, toggles, sliders, charts and more alongside the Bryntum Calendar. Cut clicks and searching to meet user needs faster. Wire up and style widgets straightforwardly via our clear docs.",
